Install VS Code

1. Navigate to the VS Code download page and download the correct installer
2. Launch the installer and walk through the steps to install VS Code.
3. Open VS Code, navigate to the VS Code Extension Marketplace, and install REditorSupport

4. Open a new text file.
5. Change the text file language to R in the Select Language Mode menu (link in botton right)

6. VS Code will prompt you to install languageserver; agree to the prompt
